c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Ahrefs and NeuronWriter share a solid foundation of core features including Keyword Research, Content Optimization, Competitor Analysis, Ai Writing. Where Ahrefs pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Rank Tracking and Site Audit and Backlink Analysis and Reporting and Api Access, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Ahrefs holds an overall score of 9/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while NeuronWriter scores 7/10 overall and 6/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
d:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, NeuronWriter comes in at a lower starting price of $23/mo, while Ahrefs begins at $129/mo. Neither platform offers a free plan, so you will need to budget for at least the starting tier from the beginning. Be sure to take advantage of any trial periods they may offer."}]]}]
