10:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Ahrefs is best suited for link builders, SEO agencies, content marketers, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. NeuronWriter, meanwhile, shines for budget SEOs, content writers, bloggers, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2010, Ahrefs describes itself as \"Comprehensive SEO toolset known for the best backlink index in the industry.\" NeuronWriter, established in 2021, positions itself as \"NLP-based content optimization and AI writing tool for SEO.\" With 11 years between them, Ahrefs brings the maturity and proven track record of a veteran platform, while NeuronWriter offers the fresh perspective and modern architecture of a newer entrant."}]]}]
11:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Ahrefs** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (9.0 vs 7.0), more features (10 vs 5). However, this does not mean NeuronWriter is a poor choice — far from it. NeuronWriter excels in its own right, particularly for budget SEOs and content writers.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value best backlink database in the industry, go with Ahrefs. If very affordable nlp content optimization matters more to you, NeuronWriter is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
